OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHMRC drops decision to     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fclose self-assessment      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fhelpline                   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, HM Revenue and Customs (HMRC) has      
OL,6, reversed a decision to close its       
OL,7, self-assessment telephone helpline for 
OL,8, half of the year.                      
OL,10,FThe tax authority announced on Tuesday 
OL,11,Fthat the line would be closed between  
OL,12,FApril and September, with taxpayers    
OL,13,Fdirected to online services instead.   
OL,15,FBut less than a day later it said the  
OL,16,Fphone line would stay open this summer.
OL,18,F"The pace of this change needs to match
OL,19,Fthe public appetite for managing their 
OL,20,Ftax affairs online," its boss said.    
